    "body": "It looks like you may be using an outdated version of web3.js?  And it is trying to trigger a transaction instead of invoking `balanceOf` via `eth_call`.\r\n\r\nin the latest version, it looks like you want to use this method: https://web3js.readthedocs.io/en/v1.7.4/web3-eth-contract.html#methods-mymethod-call .",
